. Field Definitions
. -----------------
.
. Field     Type            Length    From - To      Description
.---------------------------------------------------------------------------
CHST       RECORD
Entity     DIM               8          1 - 8
CustomerID DIM               6          9 - 14
CustFill   DIM               4         15 - 18
Year       DIM               4         19 - 22
PurchAmt   FORM              10.2(13)  23 - 191      //1-12 (Jan-Dec), 13=YTD
PaidAmt    FORM              10.2(13) 192 - 360      //1-12 (Jan-Dec), 13=YTD
PurchTotal FORM              4(13)    361 - 412      //1-12 (Jan-Dec), 13=YTD
PaidTotal  FORM              4(13)    413 - 464      //1-12 (Jan-Dec), 13=YTD
DiscAmt    FORM              10.2(13) 465 - 633      //1-12 (Jan-Dec), 13=YTD
LastPayDt  DIM               8        634 - 641      //Last Payment Date
LastPayAmt FORM              7.2      642 - 651      //Last Payment Amount
LastCheck  DIM               10       652 - 661      //Last Check Number
           RECORDEND
